                            <comment id="17192389" author="edimitrova" created="Tue, 8 Sep 2020 18:34:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=samt&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;samt&quot;&gt;samt&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank you for the patch!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will do a review later today.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One thing I was thinking around the flakiness - can you loop the test with the patch like 10 times(10 should be enough if it was failing consistently I guess) or something in your environment? (Or you already did that?)&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17192523" author="edimitrova" created="Tue, 8 Sep 2020 23:10:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch looks good to me. &#160;Unfortunately, we rely on timing, so as suggested in my previous comment, please, loop it to check for flakiness.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17192787" author="beobal" created="Wed, 9 Sep 2020 10:58:47 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;can you loop the test with the patch like 10 times&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;yep, I did that already and saw no failures.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the review &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=e.dimitrova&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;e.dimitrova&quot;&gt;e.dimitrova&lt;/a&gt;, committed to trunk in &lt;tt&gt;c6fc6714eea73d94e6befd13b52a15cd48e28f7a&lt;/tt&gt; with the typo fixed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
